name: Observation: Dispersal
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show Xenia teleporting in a style you do not recognise.

name: Observation: Arrival
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show Xenia arriving, alone, in this chamber.

name: Observation: Correction
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to be footage of me repairing something.

name: Observation: Transition
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This is a before and after of the Wen mouthpiece - broken and then repaired.

name: Observation: Evolution
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to be a study of the golem as its personality develops.

name: Observation: Imprinting
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show me making decisions in proximity to the golem.

name: Observation: Predator
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show Ariane constructing a device to track down Xenia.

name: Observation: Focus
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show the golem being tuned to follow Xenia.

name: Observation: Conflict
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show Ariane and Xenia's fight and subsequent interruption.

name: Observation: Condemnation
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show Ariane and I discussing Xenia's mental instability.

name: Observation: Theft
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show Xenia siphoning energy from something.

name: Observation: Innocence
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show the golem admiring a butterfly.

name: Observation: ERROR
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This doesn't show any footage. It seems to show some kind of interference.

name: Observation: Awoken
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show a large crater on a strange desolate world.

name: Observation: Husk
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show the golem before it was activated.

name: Observation: Revelry
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show...oh. That's not good.

name: Observation: Silence
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show you asleep. It's unflattering, and a bit creepy.

name: Observation: Beauty
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This is just footage of a duck.

name: Observation: Corruption
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show Ariane studying something from a book.

name: Observation: Present
examine: Crystallised clairvoyance: This seems to show me studying this observation.

name: Combined observation: Xenia was alone
examine: These combined observations prove that Xenia was alone when she teleported into the chamber using a spell only she knows.

name: Combined observation: We stand apart
examine: These combined observations prove that I have been acting counter to Xenia's aims and have been repairing the damage she has caused.

name: Combined observation: Golem and I
examine: These combined observations prove that the golem and I are working together and share a bond of friendship.

name: Combined observation: Ariane and the golem
examine: These combined observations prove that Ariane created the golem for the purpose of tracking down Xenia.

name: Combined observation: The madness of friends
examine: These combined observations prove that we believe Xenia has become dangerously disturbed and that we are attempting to stop her.

name: Combined observation: United we stand
examine: These combined observations prove that the golem, myself and Ariane are standing apart from Xenia and working to stop her.

name: Combined observation: Elder stalker
examine: These combined observations prove that the mouthpiece is a little too interested in what you get up to.

name: Combined observation: Xenia is harming the mouthpiece
examine: These combined observations show that Xenia is causing damage by draining energy from something.

name: Combined observation: The mouthpiece can observe events
examine: These combined observations show that the mouthpiece can observe events over time.

name: Combined observation: Ariane is studious
examine: These combined observations show that Ariane is extremely skilled in the arcane arts.

name: Combined observation: Xenia is avoiding detection
examine: These combined observations show that Xenia is capable of avoiding detection by the mouthpiece.
